query:
SELECT t.id, t.token, t.isActive, t.createdAt, g.name as gp_name 
FROM gp_access_tokens t 
JOIN game_presenters g ON t.gamePresenterId = g.id 
WHERE t.isActive = 1 AND g.name LIKE '%Agnes%';
